Grep:
Search text.
grep nginx /var/log/syslog

Awk:
Print specific columns.
awk '{print $1}'

Sed:
Replace text.
sed 's/dev/test/g' file.txt

Sort:
sort file.txt

Unique Values:
uniq file.txt

Cut:
cut -d ":" -f1 /etc/passwd

Real-Time Scenario:
Find failed logins.
grep "Failed password" /var/log/auth.log
